<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900913-0150</DOCNO><DOCID>900913-0150.</DOCID><HL>   Pier 1 Sales Increase</HL><DATE>09/13/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C9</SO><CO>   PIR</CO><IN>SPECIALTY RETAILERS (OTS)</IN><LP>   FORT WORTH, Texas -- Pier 1 Imports Inc. said sales forthe second quarter ended Sept.2 increased 11%, to $149.6million from $134.9 million. Sales at stores open more than ayear increased 4.1%. Pier One is a specialty retailer of homefurnishings.   ---</LP><TEXT>   Corrections andamp; Amplifications                                                                                                          PIER 1 IMPORTS Inc.'s sales for the second quarter endedSept. 2 at stores open at least one year declined 4.1%. Thefigure was given as an increase in yesterday's edition.   (WSJ Sept. 14, 1990)</TEXT></DOC>